# Session telemetry (per-machine)
docs/analytics/

# Visual-regression baselines — moved to local bucket (~/.openread-dev/artifacts/).
# See /migrate-baselines and docs/probe-driven-workflow-implementation.md §7.7.
e2e/**/*.spec.ts-snapshots/
**/__snapshots__/*.png
# ...except the per-feature manifest, which is committed so CI can reproduce
# the expected baseline set.
!docs/design/**/baselines.manifest.json
